high_descs: Go right and then right again and face the black desk with the box.
Pick the phone on the right up from the desk.
Turn around and go left to face the box on the gray couch.
Put the phone in the box.
Pick the box up from the couch.
Turn and face the chair to the left.
Put the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a phone in it on a chair.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the left side of the desk, the long side.
Pick up cell phone closest to the corner of the desk.
Turn around and veer left before the coffee table, towards the box on the couch.
Place the phone in the box.
Pick up the box.
Turn left and face the chair.
Place the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a cell phone in it on a chair.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the chair, then turn right and walk over to the black desk.
Pick up the rightmost phone off of the black desk.
Turn around and walk over to the couch with the cardboard box on it.
Put the phone into the cardboard box on the couch.
Pick up the cardboard box with the phone in it.
Turn around and walk up to the coffee table, then turn right and walk up to the chair.
Put the cardboard box with the phone in it on the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a phone in it on the seat of a chair.
